Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: American embassy hostages stalemate
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b040h3xq
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 25 Nov 1979
Diplomacy rendered impotent by success of Iran's terrorist seizure of US hostages. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.